"This edition of the bootilicious series continues in the spirited and sassy vein of its predecessors. Right off the bat this one smokes, with buxom beauty Caprice showing up with a couple of gal pals (Ice Cream and Tia). They're all there to romp with massively-endowed Jack Napier, and the scene is a fun one. Each gal gets her fair share of passion, and Jack ends up as the happiest guy on the whole tape. Black Cat is a fiery newcomer to the scene who's been blazing her way straight up the carnal charts. Here, she takes on Lexington Steele in a raucous multi-position bang-up that's sure to satisfy. Another top-notch scene finds luscious Obsession and Lacy hooking up with some lucky stiff. The gals take turns driving him right through the roof, and they're both amply rewarded for their enthusiastic work. Each scene here sparkles with real energy and excitement, and the women are all very eager to please. Another rock-solid entry from one of the best all-black lines out there!"
